Interesting bar, decent size, with some bar games, and very old school. The bartender was very nice, and though we didn't fit in with the people who were patronizing the bar that night, we never felt unwelcome, or let's get out of here, or anything like that. With being old school, the prices were old school too, which was very good. My only real issue with the place was, you can only have basic cocktails, and the rest rooms could use some updating.
